<title>USA: Accent Software nets $1.85mln in placement.</title>
<headline>Accent Software nets $1.85mln in placement.</headline>
<dateline>COLORADO SPRINGS, Colo 1997-08-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Accent Software International Ltd said Wednesday it netted $1.85 million in a private placement.</p>
<p>The software developer said it completed the sale of a two-year six-percent $2 million convertible debenture and 300,000 warrants to an institutional investor. It added the debenture is convertible in common stock and 250,000 warrants were priced at $2.80 each and 50,000 priced at $3.20.</p>
<p>Accent said it would use the net proceeds to develop more software language solution products and increase marketing.</p>
